{"id":"api/common/provideCloudflareLoader","title":"provideCloudflareLoader","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/provideCloudflareLoader\", \"name\": \"provideCloudflareLoader\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/image_loaders/cloudflare_loader.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L32-L33\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/image_loaders/cloudflare_loader.ts#L32-L33\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providecloudflareloader\">provideCloudflareLoader<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/provideCloudflareLoader#providecloudflareloader\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">為<a href=\"https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/image-resizing/\">Cloudflare Image Resizing</a>產生 ImageLoader 並將其轉換為 Angular 提供程式的函式。注意：Cloudflare 有多種圖像產品——該提供商專門針對 Cloudflare Image Resizing； 它不適用於 Cloudflare Images 或 Cloudflare Polish。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Function that generates an ImageLoader for <a href=\"https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/image-resizing/\">Cloudflare Image\nResizing</a> and turns it into an Angular\nprovider. Note: Cloudflare has multiple image products - this provider is specifically for\nCloudflare Image Resizing; it will not work with Cloudflare Images or Cloudflare Polish.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/common/provideCloudflareLoader\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideCloudflareLoader</a>: (path: string) =&gt; <a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[];\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - guide/image-directive\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/provideCloudflareLoader#providecloudflareloader\n - api/core/Provider\n - https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/image-resizing/\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/image_loaders/cloudflare_loader.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L32-L33\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/image_loaders/cloudflare_loader.ts#L32-L33\n-->"}